<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Skillsync Activation Email</title>

  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      background-color: #fafafa;
      color: #222;
    }

    a {
      color: #000;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    table td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #0070f3;
      padding: 24px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #fff;
    }

    .email-footer {
      padding: 24px;
      background-color: #f6f6f6;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #0070f3;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to Skillsync</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hi <%= user.name %>,</p>
      <p>Thanks for signing up for Skillsync! We're excited to have you on board.</p>
      <p>Before you can start using Skillsync, you need to confirm your email address.</p>
      <p>Click the button below to confirm your email address:</p>
      <h2>
        <%= activationCode %>
      </h2>
      <p>If you didn't sign up for Skillsync, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Thanks,<br>The Skillsync Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>Â© 2020 Skillsync. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>